{"tid":722930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【游蕙禎出獄】游蕙禎第一句說話","createTime":"2018-06-30T03:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T13:03:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":59,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0f9072f8a1d847e2884f1e781861b387806a20","tid":722930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"【10:56】私家車在葵青區一間酒店外停下，游蕙禎與朋友進入酒店辦入住手續，並說：「我講過唔會任何回應，聽日都唔會。」<br />\n【10:12】《蘋果》聯絡到梁頌恆，他正在壁屋監獄接另一位出獄的成員。他指游蕙禎今日會與家人相聚，暫不接受傳媒訪問。<br />\n【10:05】私家車經粉錦公路、林錦公路出市區<br />\n【09:50】身穿白色長裙的游蕙禎，步出懲教所。記者問她會否參加7.1遊行，她說：「今日唔講喇、今日唔講喇！今日唔回應，唔好意思。」隨即登上白色私家車，由朋友陪同離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">早上8時，羅湖懲教所外已經有<span style=\"color: red;\">大批傳媒</span>守候。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58381300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58381300&d=iAMpvvGt5V248h%2B0dZZ%2BXtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f7a1cd25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58381300&h=7976031b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58381300</a>"},{"pid":"4c6f04989385558c8a8bc8f5d7312a85428e3fd4","tid":722930,"uid":139613,"like":21,"dislike":88,"score":-67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"冇人想g牙"},{"pid":"8c11b743e94768f0493e8eee94fc14f63e9113c4","tid":722930,"uid":19454,"like":105,"dislike":6,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"「今日唔講喇、今日唔講喇！今日唔回應，唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJ ed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfcaccb95b4e9ccafa421d2c2669b53f3ea573f","tid":722930,"uid":96,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"老貓有冇扮傳媒去接遊b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\